{"tid":738312,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"放榜後入黎講低邊個補習佬值得補 邊個狗也不屌","createTime":"2018-07-11T12:18:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T14:26:24.000Z","uid":4876,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8277d3efcf00c13b82de56c4df28fbc1579ea0ad","tid":738312,"uid":4876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:18:02.000Z","msg":"之前你地班垃圾打手一日到黑係到吹奏啲垃圾老師<br />\n今日就放榜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留低你補完覺得有用既補習佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好POST埋單同成績 如果唔係俾人當打手就無謂啦<br />\n<br />\n我先 有圖有真相 即刻幫型佬CLIFF含一含撚先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4月先黎自修elective part都有** 我愛你呀型佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/201620_e1d68a3d9abb70d433abd7cdabbbae4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F201620_e1d68a3d9abb70d433abd7cdabbbae4e.jpg&h=6536c2f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/201622_36e03e502e4f8ceea9cd01494832fbc2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F201622_36e03e502e4f8ceea9cd01494832fbc2.jpg&h=e1878374&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d0e69e95fff178320ce7d2d87f8a8d78766f5ee","tid":738312,"uid":136186,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:19:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">yy lam 狗也不屌</span></span>"},{"pid":"f88bdc0b078cea6f6e4c16571504507bf9695b15","tid":738312,"uid":4876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d0e69e95fff178320ce7d2d87f8a8d78766f5ee","tid":738312,"uid":136186,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:19:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">yy lam 狗也不屌</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:19:59.000Z","msg":"巨人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c4e9db48acd68902c28b4ab729ff5fca7ed6db","tid":738312,"uid":4876,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:27:15.000Z","msg":"講開就講多個<br />\n我都有補過食女學生既Oscar Ma兩期<br />\n我勸各位如果唔係落重注係LS到就真係唔好補OM<br />\n我唔係話佢教得差 但係佢一期係有成六堂 而每堂都個半鐘以上 有陣時兩個幾鐘<br />\n老實講你有咁多時間上LS堂既話 不如將啲時間轉去溫ELECTIVE<br />\n就算係拎黎溫中英 我都覺得有用過補LS<br />\nOM單我就冇啦 佢所有野都EMAIL SEND 我DEL晒<br />\nSMS就仲有個<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/202507_4bd3f5de317602d176504866f8929d72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F202507_4bd3f5de317602d176504866f8929d72.jpg&h=d821e068&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451220895311456294f704f7713c74b1f87b0ebc","tid":738312,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:33:01.000Z","msg":"樓主幾分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead5d7668cf7c517a975956a7b304df80708a01d","tid":738312,"uid":4876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"451220895311456294f704f7713c74b1f87b0ebc","tid":738312,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:33:01.000Z","msg":"樓主幾分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:38:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你入CU 爽爽子啦<img src=\